gtping/README

 GTP Ping

   By Thomas Habets <thomas@habets.pp.se>


Description
-----------
Like ping(8), but uses GTP ping requests to ping GGSNs and anything
else that will answer them.


License
-------
GPL, see the LICENCE file.


Compiling
---------
Run "make". This produces a "gtping" binary.


Example use
-----------
$ ./gtping -c 1 1.2.3.4
GTPing 0.13, By Thomas Habets <thomas@habets.pp.se>
GTPING 1.2.3.4 (1.2.3.4) 12 bytes of data.
12 bytes from 1.2.3.4: seq=0 time=0.51 ms

--- 1.2.3.4 GTP ping statistics ---
1 packets transmitted, 1 received, 0 dups, 0% packet loss, time 1000ms
rtt min/avg/max/mdev = 0.512/0.512/0.512/0.000 ms


